DESCRIPTION: High Voltage Fairies in the Pit The Fairy Pit opens up again in Viper Room\, starting now every last Friday of the month we are taking over the place with heavy riffs and high voltage bass drops. Grab your wings and boots and dive headfirst into the madness. Let’s start a riot\, see you in the pit! One pit to rule them all: Alternative & Nu Metal\, Metalcore + Drum and Bass Sounds Like: Electric Callboy | Bring Me the Horizon | Linkin Park | Motionless in White | Architects | Polaris | Poppy | Beartooth | Three Days Grace | Falling in Reverse | System of a Down | Slipknot | Korn | Avenged Sevenfold | Rise Against | Parkway Drive | A Day to Remember | Ice Nine Kills | Enter Shikari | Five Finger Death Punch | Lorna Shore | In Flames | Landmvrks | Bullet for My Valentine | My Chemical Romance | Black Veil Brides | Hollywood Undead | Papa Roach | Limp Bizkit | The Offspring | Jimmy Eat World | Tenacious D | Sum 41 | Skindred | Dropkick Murphys | Flogging Molly  | Pierce the Veil | Scene Queen | Thousand Foot Krutch | Pendulum | Chase & Status | The Prodigy | The Qemists | Solence | Zardonic | Kanine | Delta heavy | Camo & Krooked | Kayzo\, Bad Omens | Fox Stevenson Goodies: Gratis Eintritts-Shots und High Voltage Fairies Party Vibes mit Knicklichtern & LED-Kronen Merch Stand: Schnapp dir High Voltage Fairies (HVF) Merch günstiger als online\, mit HVF-Merch bekommst du halben Eintritt bei unseren Events! Limited Online Presale: Early Bird Tickets: 7€ Abendkassa: Im Feen-Kostüm / HVF-Merch: 6€ | Standard: 10€  
